{
  "texts": [
    "The cutoff was set to 5 for small molecules in QM9, MD17, rMD17, and Molecule3D, and changed to 4 for Chignolin in order to reduce the number of edges in the molecular graphs.",
    "For the MD22 dataset, the cutoff of relatively small molecules was set to 5, that of bigger molecules was set to 4.",
    "Cutoff was not used in the OGB-LSC PCQM4Mv2 dataset.",
    "We used the learning rate decay if the validation loss stopped decreasing.",
    "The patience was set to 5 epochs for Molecule3D, 15 epochs for QM9, and 30 epochs for MD17, rMD17, MD22, and Chignolin."
  ]
}